    "approximate computations 向け adjustable error parameters を support する sum-check extension。",
  "New prover algorithm optimizing time and space efficiency for multilinear polynomials.":
    "multilinear polynomials の time / space efficiency を最適化する新しい prover algorithm。",
  "Significant reduction in computation costs related to equality factors in sumcheck.":
    "sumcheck の equality factors に関連する computation costs を大幅に削減。",
  "GPU preprocessing technique improving MSM algorithm efficiency for ZKP systems.":
    "ZKP systems 向け MSM algorithm efficiency を改善する GPU preprocessing technique。",
  "GKR protocol-based folding scheme reducing vector commitment size per fold step.":
    "fold step ごとの vector commitment size を削減する GKR protocol-based folding scheme。",
  "Scalable system verifying machine learning model fairness through ZK technology.":
    "ZK technology により machine learning model fairness を verify する scalable system。",
  "Dynamic constraint generation improving proof generation efficiency and flexibility.":
    "proof generation efficiency と flexibility を改善する dynamic constraint generation。",
  "Generic framework for verifiable deep learning with linear proving time.":
    "linear proving time を持つ verifiable deep learning の generic framework。",
  "Verifying LLM output authenticity using sumcheck, proving 1.3B parameter models in 15 minutes.":
    "sumcheck を使って LLM output authenticity を verify し、1.3B parameter models を 15 分で prove します。",
  "Image transformation verification supporting various operations with folding zkSNARK.":
    "folding zkSNARK でさまざまな operations を support する image transformation verification。",
  "WARP: The first linear-time accumulator with logarithmic verifier time.":
    "logarithmic verifier time を持つ最初の linear-time accumulator、WARP。",
  "Unified framework covering standard, projection, index, vector and decomposable lookups.":
    "standard、projection、index、vector、decomposable lookups を扱う unified framework。",
  "Hash function for binary extension fields compatible with Binius proof systems.":
    "Binius proof systems と compatible な binary extension fields 向け hash function。",
  "Constraint-friendly mapping achieving 23x constraint reduction and 50-100x proof speedup.":
    "23x constraint reduction と 50-100x proof speedup を実現する constraint-friendly mapping。",
