    "storage overhead を最適化する locally repairable codes based DAS repair framework。",
  "Disproved multiple RS proximity gap conjectures affecting FRI and DEEP-FRI security.":
    "FRI と DEEP-FRI security に影響する複数の RS proximity gap conjectures を反証。",
  "General attack method showing small-field hash SNARGs have lower security than expected.":
    "small-field hash SNARGs の security が想定より低いことを示す general attack method。",
  "A new approach to iO.": "iO への新しい approach。",
  "Practical MPC preprocessing model with one-time setup for efficient online computation.":
    "efficient online computation のための one-time setup を持つ practical MPC preprocessing model。",
  "Efficient threshold FHE decryption with 20,000x online throughput improvement.":
    "online throughput を 20,000x 改善する efficient threshold FHE decryption。",
  "Optimistic smart contract protocol using garbled circuits for fraud proofs.":
    "fraud proofs に garbled circuits を使う optimistic smart contract protocol。",
