    "performance testing と Docker support を含む 25 個の ZKP frameworks の survey。",
  "Systematic survey of privacy protocols in blockchain with design recommendations.":
    "design recommendations を含む blockchain privacy protocols の systematic survey。",
  "Comprehensive analysis of code-based cryptography for post-quantum security.":
    "post-quantum security 向け code-based cryptography の comprehensive analysis。",
